moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9dc1787be0cbd462da245e4b24f451bfc6a618","tid":310862,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"推...食左藥10年....想戒甩佢...."},{"pid":"ec1a9ce749ff29267de591b989f0707cdd072ebf","tid":310862,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老味你班垃圾精神科西醫畜同心理畜同社畜<br />\n<br />\n全部都係廢物賤畜<br />\n<br />\n食咁多西藥肝腎傷晒<br />\n<br />\n所以冇食好耐<br />\n<br />\n呢世都唔會再食落肚<br />\n<br />\n認同上面果位講<br />\n<br />\n我會去睇某中醫同埋儲錢做gym<br />\n<br />\n運動係屋企有少少做到<br />\n<br />\ngym真係要出去<br />\n<br />\n身體好心理先可以提升到<br />\n<br />\n我係身體極差心理極差"},{"pid":"f9e6308dcd41f7b39e854d9fb29bdfac5589f271","tid":310862,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e73335e7e5e73a6f92e81263b8bac65a10dabd85","tid":310862,"uid":52415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推...食左藥10年....想戒甩佢....</blockquote><br />\n你唔食會點呀？"},{"pid":"0cf1128645ab736c53141f6cd7858dca6722b02e","tid":310862,"uid":52415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁我係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係行家"}]}